zem z HUNTR/X i Saja Boys. Pełna wersja karaoke hitowego filmu Netflixa w kinach tylko 10-18 czerwca.\n\nGwiazdy K-popu Rumi, Mira i Zoey w przerwach między koncertami na pełnych stadionach bronią fanów przed nadnaturalnymi zagrożeniami, korzystając ze swoich tajemnych mocy.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"9212e3f5-252f-4d08-b375-2923037a4591","name":"animowany","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/loBwcgZt_m4"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/KPopoweLowczynieplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow8.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"10","value":"10","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke w Helios na Scenie","link":null,"screeningId":"e81b378a-f63c-4043-93cc-ed7a24401aeb","screenId":"274c4d10-6f11-4c6d-943d-8be6a5eadf47","cinemaId":"c21c6e3b-874c-4432-b44e-a155ec9102cd","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T13:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T14:46:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-13T13:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-13T12:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":163,"audience":6,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":2868677,"items":[{"movieId":"4c6e0734-8000-45cf-9abe-161ae1a5ff6e","moviePrintId":"d882e05d-f8ef-4987-ba35-fb379d34fca7","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T13:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T14:46:00+02:00","movieName":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"274c4d10-6f11-4c6d-943d-8be6a5eadf47","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":6,"symbol":"HELIOS NA SCENIE","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"9fa84454-3318-4d8f-bd42-0125bcba84ca","duration":130,"description":"Polly i Tim wraz z trójką dzieci stają przed koniecznością przeprowadzenia się na odludną angielską prowincję. Wkrótce po przyjeździe najmłodsi odkrywają niezwykłe drzewo, zamieszkane przez barwne, ekscentryczne postacie. Jeśli odważą się wspiąć na jego szczyt, czekają na nie fantastyczne krainy, pełne zapierających dech przygód.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"726b5445-9bb2-48ff-8ef1-c4e96bb92399","name":"przygodowy","description":""},{"id":"6bcd8fba-fbc2-466a-9f37-ce7a42443c2e","name":"familijny","description":""},{"id":"32d53995-2198-4b43-aa57-235bfeee409e","name":"fantasy","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/T1FJ-tzNDXc"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/DRZEWOMAGIITEASERPLAKAT(1).png"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii7(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii6(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii5(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii4(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii3(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii2(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drzewomagii1(1).jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"8","value":"8","description":"od lat 8"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/DUB","name":"Drzewo Magii - KNT","link":null,"screeningId":"0585d52d-1c28-4fc9-bf29-b7e94a4b52b4","screenId":"a0433da9-b091-41ef-8eb7-c7a9eefe3af3","cinemaId":"c21c6e3b-874c-4432-b44e-a155ec9102cd","timeFrom":"2026-06-11T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-11T11:10:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-11T09:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-11T08:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":112,"audience":32,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":74222365,"items":[{"movieId":"f222b6a2-1b42-430c-80f9-f93e67d877b5","moviePrintId":"536eb5ef-6dba-4724-8783-7e90a5b0e9f5","timeFrom":"2026-06-11T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-11T11:10:00+02:00","movieName":"Drzewo magii","speakingType":"DUB","printType":"2D","screenId":"a0433da9-b091-41ef-8eb7-c7a9eefe3af3","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":7,"symbol":"KINO NA TEMAT","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"e362bc3f-0996-4255-9b93-01b948a58580","duration":108,"description":"","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"9212e3f5-252f-4d08-b375-2923037a4591","name":"animowany","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/dExv55xsVEg"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kurozajacplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/KurozajaciSwiatyniaSwistaka7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/KurozajaciSwiatyniaSwistaka6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/KurozajaciSwiatyniaSwistaka5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/KurozajaciSwiatyniaSwistaka4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/KurozajaciSwiatyniaSwistaka2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/KurozajaciSwiatyniaSwistaka1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"7","value":"7","description":"od lat 7"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/DUB","name":"Kurozając i Świątynia Świstaka - KNTJ","link":null,"screeningId":"58f7cb19-4334-4256-b80c-ebef76d6331e","screenId":"a0433da9-b091-41ef-8eb7-c7a9eefe3af3","cinemaId":"c21c6e3b-874c-4432-b44e-a155ec9102cd","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T10:48:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-10T09:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-10T08:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":112,"audience":32,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":1125666,"items":[{"movieId":"0bb27dc4-4800-473a-9ff4-a8c65ee7bf4a","moviePrintId":"b946fb4a-1034-427a-a6bb-f380499f1278","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T10:48:00+02:00","movieName":"Kurozając i Świątynia Świstaka","speakingType":"DUB","printType":"2D","screenId":"a0433da9-b091-41ef-8eb7-c7a9eefe3af3","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":8,"symbol":"KINO NA TEMAT JUNIOR","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"ed834156-8c3f-4332-8f23-3c9b0648811c","duration":108,"description":"Makoto jest zwyczajną nastolatką, spędzającą większość czasu z przyjaciółmi. Kiedy pewnego dnia, spiesząc się z wizytą do ciotki, cudem unika potrącenia przez pociąg – przeskakuje w czasie do momentu sprzed wypadku. Korzystając z nowo poznanych zdolności, naprawia swoje codzienne błędy – od słabych ocen na sprawdzianach po nieudane wyznania miłości. Kiedy jednak dosięgają ją konsekwencje manipulowania czasem, Makoto musi zrobić wszystko, żeby uniknąć straszliwej przyszłości, której nie da się cofnąć.\nOdkryj na nowo film nominowanego do Oscara reżysera Mamoru Hosoda „O dziewczynie skaczącej przez czas” na wielkim ekranie, odnowiony w oszałamiającej jakości 4K.\nWIDZOWIE POKAZÓW W RAMACH PROJEKTU HELIOS ANIME OTRZYMAJĄ ","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"ecd4a997-2c14-4fd9-98c2-53ac7087a9bc","name":"anime","description":""}],"trailers":[],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Dziewczynaskaczacaplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"13","value":"13","description":"od lat 13"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"O dziewczynie skaczącej przez czas w Helios Anime","link":null,"screeningId":"74c30641-9d96-44db-9c60-000303ae58ac","screenId":"6cea83f6-a365-4aed-86d8-672786c1bfb3","cinemaId":"c21c6e3b-874c-4432-b44e-a155ec9102cd","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T15:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T17:18:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-13T16:00:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-13T14:30:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":163,"audience":45,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":54245687,"items":[{"movieId":"9119aa2a-c2cf-4c37-bb76-918faec77850","moviePrintId":"d8e8e674-b775-49f5-8bf8-f210118ecf7d","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T15:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T17:18:00+02:00","movieName":"O dziewczynie skaczącej przez czas","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"6cea83f6-a365-4aed-86d8-672786c1bfb3","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":13,"symbol":"HELIOS ANIME","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"1383831a-42da-445a-807a-4a974a75c874","duration":134,"description":"Andrea to utalentowany uczeń włoskiej szkoły, który śpiewa również w chórze. Staje się to powodem drwin wśród rówieśników. Przewodzi im Christian, najprzystojniejszy chłopak w szkole. Andrea pada ofiarą przemocy psychicznej i nie potrafi sobie z tym poradzić. ","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dra